name: Gesturelistener.js
tagline: A Javascript gesture library loosely based on a pointers abstraction layer
body:
# GestureListener.js
A Javascript gesture library that works on a variety of devices and browsers.  Tested in recent versions of IE, Chrome, and Safari, as well as on Ipad, Iphone, and Android devices.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
